<br>
From others' posts on this board, one person posted that SU3 was a 17% damage increase against undead.<br>
<br>
As far as hits go, with my Fiery Defender I've seen hits from about 714 up to well over 3000, I think I've seen theories on the formula for max slay hits posted here as just short of 100x the base weapon damage.<br>
<br>
I think against undead mobs this puts us on par or above most damage dealing classes, but this will vary a lot based on the situation.  Luclin mobs tend to have pretty high AC and damage mitigation so having hits for 700+ on up can make a big difference on some of the Luclin undead boss mobs.<br>
<br>
I don't worry so much about whether I'm outdamaging someone else though, I just enjoy having the skill.<br>
<br>
It can be a long road getting there, but I think most people who have completed it are happy they did. <p><BR>
